#. [topic]: id=editor_tool_paint
#: data/core/editor/help.cfg:29
msgid ""
"Paint terrain tiles on the map.\n"
"The paint tool utilizes the brush sizes and the terrain palette.\n"
"\n"
"<header>Keyboard Modifiers</header>\n"
"• Shift+mouse click: If a base terrain is selected, change the base without "
"changing the overlay. If an overlay is selected, change the overlay without "
"changing the base.\n"
"• Control+mouse click: Select the terrain under the mouse cursor, as if it "
"had been selected on the terrain palette (picks up both base and overlay).\n"
"\n"
"<header>Brush Sizes</header>\n"
"The selected brush changes the size of the tool:"
msgstr ""
"Pinta celas do terreo no mapa.\n"
"A ferramenta de pintura utiliza os tamaños do pincel e a paleta do terreo.\n"
"\n"
"<header>Modificadores de teclado</header>\n"
"• Maiús+clic do rato: se se selecciona un terreo base, cambia a base sen "
"cambiar a superposición. Se se selecciona unha superposición, cambia a "
"superposición sen cambiar a base.\n"
"• Control+clic do rato: selecciona o terreo debaixo do cursor do rato, coma "
"se estivese seleccionado na paleta do terreo (recolle tanto a base como a "
"superposición).\n"
"\n"
"<header>Tamaños de pincel</header>\n"
"O pincel seleccionado cambia o tamaño da ferramenta:"

